<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="fr">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>CV - DJEKOURMAN ALLADOUM MIKE</title>
    <style>
        * { margin: 0; padding: 0; box-sizing: border-box; }
        body {
            font-family: 'Segoe UI', Tahoma, Geneva, Verdana, sans-serif;
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #1a1f3a 0%, #0a0e27 100%);
            color: #333;
            padding: 20px;
        }
        .container {
            max-width: 900px;
            margin: 0 auto;
            background: white;
            padding: 40px;
            border-radius: 10px;
            box-shadow: 0 10px 40px rgba(0,0,0,0.2);
        }
        .header {
            border-bottom: 3px solid #00d9ff;
            padding-bottom: 20px;
            margin-bottom: 30px;
            text-align: center;
        }
        .header h1 {
            font-size: 2.5em;
            color: #0a0e27;
            margin-bottom: 5px;
        }
        .header p {
            font-size: 1.2em;
            color: #b344ff;
            margin: 5px 0;
        }
        .contact-info {
            display: flex;
            justify-content: center;
            gap: 20px;
            flex-wrap: wrap;
            font-size: 0.9em;
            margin-top: 10px;
        }
        .contact-info span {
            color: #666;
        }
        .section {
            margin-bottom: 30px;
        }
        .section h2 {
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #00d9ff, #b344ff);
            color: white;
            padding: 10px 15px;
            border-radius: 5px;
            margin-bottom: 15px;
            font-size: 1.3em;
        }
        .subsection {
            margin-bottom: 15px;
            padding-left: 20px;
            border-left: 3px solid #00d9ff;
        }
        .subsection h3 {
            color: #0a0e27;
            margin-bottom: 5px;
        }
        .subsection .meta {
            color: #b344ff;
            font-size: 0.9em;
            font-weight: bold;
            margin-bottom: 5px;
        }
        .subsection p {
            color: #666;
            line-height: 1.6;
            margin: 5px 0;
        }
        .skills-grid {
            display: grid;
            grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(250px, 1fr));
            gap: 15px;
        }
        .skill-box {
            background: #f5f5f5;
            padding: 15px;
            border-radius: 5px;
            border-left: 4px solid #ff344f;
        }
        .skill-box h4 {
            color: #0a0e27;
            margin-bottom: 8px;
        }
        .skill-box p {
            color: #666;
            font-size: 0.9em;
            line-height: 1.5;
        }
        .print-button {
            text-align: center;
            margin-top: 30px;
            padding-top: 30px;
            border-top: 1px solid #eee;
        }
        .print-button button {
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #00d9ff, #b344ff);
            color: white;
            padding: 12px 30px;
            border: none;
            border-radius: 5px;
            font-size: 1em;
            cursor: pointer;
            transition: transform 0.3s;
        }
        .print-button button:hover {
            transform: scale(1.05);
        }
        @media print {
            body { background: white; }
            .print-button { display: none; }
            .container { box-shadow: none; }
        }
        @media (max-width: 768px) {
            .container { padding: 20px; }
            .header h1 { font-size: 1.8em; }
            .contact-info { gap: 10px; font-size: 0.8em; }
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="container">
        <div class="header">
            <h1>DJEKOURMAN ALLADOUM MIKE</h1>
            <p>Web3 Developer & Blockchain Engineer</p>
            <div class="contact-info">
                <span>📱 +228 92361187</span>
                <span>📧 contact@mikealladoum.com</span>
                <span>🌐 mikealladoum.com</span>
                <span>📍 Lomé, Togo</span>
            </div>
        </div>

        <div class="section">
            <h2>👋 PROFIL PROFESSIONNEL</h2>
            <p>Développeur blockchain junior passionné par la création de solutions Web3 sécurisées et innovantes. Fort d'une expertise en Solidity, Solana et protocoles DeFi, je suis engagé dans le développement d'applications décentralisées de haute qualité. Doté d'une capacité à livrer des projets complexes avec attention au détail.</p>
